status: draft
system: LifePlanner
layer: 080.policy
subfolder: 070.settings-defaults
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero
schema: life

purpose:
  - 設定画面で扱う主要既定値を定義する
  - notification, display, review assist の初期値を揃える
  - 初回利用時の迷いを減らす

policy:
  - defaults should be helpful but not intrusive
  - users can later reduce noise
  - family-sensitive defaults should stay conservative
